### Mini Social Feed API Test Collection
### Run these requests in order.
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

@username = test
@email = {{username}}@example.com
@password = password123
@fcmToken = fake-fcm-token

### 1) Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health



### 2) Signup (creates a fresh user each run)
# @name signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"username": "{{username}}",
	"email": "{{email}}",
	"password": "{{password}}"
}



### Capture auth token from signup response
@token = {{signup.response.body.data.token}}

### 3) Login (same user)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "{{email}}",
	"password": "{{password}}"
}



### Optional: replace token with login token
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}


### 4) Get current user profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 5) Update FCM token
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/fcm-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
	"fcmToken": "{{fcmToken}}"
}



### 6) Create post
# @name createPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
	"content": "Hello I am from  {{username}}_3!"
}



### Capture new post id
@postId = {{createPost.response.body.data.post._id}}



### 7) Get posts (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### 8) Get posts (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### 9) Get posts filtered by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts?username={{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### 10) Like/unlike a post (toggle)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/69bbf2db849e360e839f6cb9/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### 11) Add comment to a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/69bbf2db849e360e839f6cb9/comment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
	"text": "Great post! Tested via REST client."
}

### 12) Negative test: Unauthorized profile request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me



### 13) Negative test: Validation error on create post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
	"content": ""
}



### 14) Negative test: Like invalid/nonexistent post id
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/000000000000000000000000/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
